org.eclipse.californium.core.coap

Class EmptyMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.californium.core.coap.Message
      • org.eclipse.californium.core.coap.EmptyMessage

  • public class EmptyMessage
extends Message
    EmptyMessage represents an empty CoAP message. An empty message has either the message CoAP.Type ACK or RST.
